"{\"reviewRef\":\"refs/heads/amshali/fatal-harmful\",\"targetRef\":\"refs/heads/master\",\"requester\":\"amshali@google.com\",\"reviewers\":[\"bstanley\",\"kfishkin\"],\"description\":\"log.Fatal considered harmful. use of log.Fatal in git mirror tool is dangerous and harmful. git mirror must be very tolerant of errors and gracefully handle them. Due to different errors in database data or comment data git mirror operations can fail at different places. When we do log.Fatal the git mirror program exits and cancel the who operation. Running it again would not help because it will fail again at the same point.\"}"
